WEBVTT

00:00:00.483 --> 00:00:03.587
(Haya mazungumzo yana mambo pevu)

00:00:04.905 --> 00:00:06.960
Kila wakati naulizwa unafanya kazi gani.

00:00:08.048 --> 00:00:09.300
Na ninajibu,

00:00:09.324 --> 00:00:12.187
"Ninafanya kazi kutokomeza ukatili 
dhidi ya watoto.

00:00:12.211 --> 00:00:15.878
Ukatili wote dhidi ya watoto wote
katika nchi zote."

00:00:16.632 --> 00:00:18.267
Kawaida kunakuwa na ukimya.

00:00:18.291 --> 00:00:20.529
Maranyingine, kulingana na mazingira,

00:00:20.553 --> 00:00:22.785
"Oh, hiyo inaua mazungumzo."

00:00:23.716 --> 00:00:25.438
Halafu maswali:

00:00:25.462 --> 00:00:27.684
"Ukatili wa aina gani
unaozungumzia?"

00:00:27.708 --> 00:00:29.184
"Kuna ukatili kiasi gani?"

00:00:29.208 --> 00:00:32.065
"Inatokea maeneo gani,
inatokea hapa?"